The paper proposes a color texture classification approach using local binary patterns, which is a common technique in computer vision and falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The proposed approach also involves a significant points selection algorithm, which is related to feature selection and could fall under the machine learning (cs.MM) or information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of AND operation for combining color sensor information, which could be related to logic in computer science (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
